Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.27,0:00:07.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每年都會變得愈加沉悶炎熱的這個暑假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.40,0:00:13.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是真要是說日本列島正在熱帶化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.20,0:00:15.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大概沒那種可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.78,0:00:19.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這讓我揮之不去的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.41,0:00:24.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很大可能是起因於我的心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.04,0:00:26.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.67,0:00:34.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.97,0:00:36.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那位長門和我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.89,0:00:39.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,共度了步入夏季之前的那段短暫時光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.68,0:00:43.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她把自己想說的都說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.77,0:00:50.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且沒有留給我回答的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.98,0:00:51.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就那樣消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.11,0:00:58.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要在意起那個時候的告白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.91,0:01:00.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對現在的長門就開不了口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.95,0:01:04.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從那之後總覺得有些不自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.63,0:01:18.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 這是…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.56,0:01:23.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是那個意…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.73,0:01:27.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.90,0:01:29.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有及時注意到 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.86,0:01:38.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓長門難堪了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.50,0:03:17.46,Title - blur - 0,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(1552,880)\bord0\blur10\fad(695,695)}煙火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.50,0:03:17.46,Title - 0,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(1552,880)\fad(695,695)}煙火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.29,0:03:17.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暑假已經過了一半了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用富士山來打比方的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.59,0:03:21.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該是在半山腰的位置吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.51,0:03:23.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話雖如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想去山腰的話好像只需要坐車就能到達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從那裡開始才算是真正的登山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是以現在的心境來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一點也感覺不到暑假正值盛期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿虛 有電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不說我也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.41,0:03:46.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.74,0:03:48.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.29,0:03:49.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你今天很閒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那又怎樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.04,0:03:54.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兩點整 在咖啡店集合 over
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.26,0:04:03.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個也完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.26,0:04:03.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.39,0:04:05.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個也做過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.55,0:04:06.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.72,0:04:09.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是之前在社團教室裡說過的計劃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.81,0:04:12.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定要在這個夏天之內做完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個需要在下周完成 古泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.44,0:04:17.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個夏天真是夠忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.86,0:04:25.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果是富士山的話大概在半山腰的位置吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.41,0:04:29.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟糕 竟然會和這傢伙有同樣的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.79,0:04:32.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是說現在開始才是真正的夏天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.46,0:04:36.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,高二的暑假只有一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趁現在盡情享受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你還沒有玩夠嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.46,0:04:41.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,僅僅只有一次的暑假嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.19,0:04:59.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下起雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.65,0:05:02.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼宮 帶傘了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.44,0:05:04.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.15,0:05:07.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不愧是涼宮 準備周全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.78,0:05:08.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼明天見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到車站前集合 別遲到喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.58,0:05:17.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝倉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.08,0:05:20.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她說有雨之日的促銷活動 先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.84,0:05:22.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.34,0:05:29.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你沒有帶傘過來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.56,0:05:31.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.35,0:05:33.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.69,0:05:44.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一起回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總是會不自覺的在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒辦法正常的對話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.18,0:06:13.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底說什麼才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.27,0:06:18.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雨 停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.94,0:06:25.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.49,0:06:27.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.40,0:06:31.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和之前的螢火蟲一樣漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.29,0:06:35.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣下去不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.08,0:06:36.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暑假才過去一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有剩下的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.34,0:06:43.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我該做些行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.63,0:06:45.84,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去泳池
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.42,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跳盂蘭盆舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.05,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.34,0:06:50.68,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天文觀測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.30,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,釣虎魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.43,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,擊球練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.38,0:06:46.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是在這之後我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.26,0:06:50.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就像瞬間被吃掉的蕎麥面一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.26,0:06:54.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不得不跟著涼宮制定的計劃過日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.22,0:07:00.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,轉眼間時間就過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.94,0:07:09.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}太好了 全壘打 全壘打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.69,0:07:10.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,情緒跟打數一樣高啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.99,0:07:12.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是有精神的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.87,0:07:17.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 下一發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.33,0:07:17.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那傢伙是真的熱血吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.59,0:07:26.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝比奈學姐 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 揮動的太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再稍微把棒球棒握短一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.77,0:07:40.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我倒是說出口啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,句惡 明明就有什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.20,0:07:53.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混賬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.78,0:07:55.83,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,擊球練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.79,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,保齡球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.41,0:08:01.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全倒 耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.66,0:08:02.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是精彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就是朝全中去的 當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.50,0:08:11.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那之後我和長門之間沒有什麼對話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暑假就這樣快過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.22,0:08:16.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別灰心 長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重振精神再來一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.97,0:08:21.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒錯 長門 現在才剛開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.93,0:08:23.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有很多挽回的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.02,0:08:26.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我倒是說出口啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.36,0:08:32.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吶 下一個是阿虛你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.95,0:08:43.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這樣根本算不上在比賽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.75,0:08:47.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了算了 涼宮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.88,0:08:50.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個缺口可以算是很難的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哼 說到底都是幹勁的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.18,0:08:56.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別太用力 自然一點扔出去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.18,0:08:59.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說不定能取得好結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒想到你能說出這句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.72,0:09:02.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不僅限於保齡球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太過於在意的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反而會偏離目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.35,0:09:08.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說不定這種情況很常見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.52,0:09:11.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上啊 古泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要把北高隊伍完全比下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.78,0:09:15.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.53,0:09:23.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,耶 漂亮的全倒 做的真不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.58,0:09:24.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,慚愧慚愧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.04,0:09:27.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在疲於奔波中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暑假也漸漸過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.00,0:09:34.47,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煙火大會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,活動也僅剩下一點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.84,0:09:39.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明是當地的小祭典
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,卻相當熱鬧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.39,0:09:44.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為日本人喜歡祭典啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 已經在買東西吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.69,0:09:50.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來了來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喜歡祭典的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,終於來了啊 真遲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.03,0:10:02.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.79,0:10:04.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,穿上這個可費了不少工夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看 怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.12,0:10:10.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,衣服會起皺折的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三位都很合身呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.09,0:10:15.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.13,0:10:21.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這也算是夏日風情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.80,0:10:22.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.76,0:10:26.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說回來 浴衣是跟鶴屋學姐借的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.77,0:10:27.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.81,0:10:28.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是嚇到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比起一般的小店 品種豐富得多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實她說要送給我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.23,0:10:35.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是涼子卻拒絕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.11,0:10:37.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.82,0:10:41.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種布料在普通商場可買不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.66,0:10:45.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我總是在擔心能不能不弄髒的還回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想的真多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鶴屋學姐和朝比奈學姐去哪裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那兩個人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.30,0:10:57.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,實物示範？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.59,0:10:58.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,路上確實有那種攤子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.22,0:11:04.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在賣連手機都能粉碎的攪拌機呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.23,0:11:11.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個人很容易著迷於郵購推銷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.44,0:11:14.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鶴屋學姐的苦笑可是難得一見喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是這樣 她叫我們先出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.07,0:11:23.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是說讓我們先隨意逛逛夜店是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.49,0:11:24.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.03,0:11:26.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 首先是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,撈金魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.75,0:11:29.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 真是的 涼宮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛說完就這樣 會起皺折的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一次多少錢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.54,0:11:36.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,300日元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.80,0:11:39.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 給我牢固的網
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.76,0:11:40.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.93,0:11:42.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,頭髮真礙事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.80,0:11:45.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼子 幫我綁頭髮 快點快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當初穿衣服的時候不是說不用了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.68,0:11:50.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個時候是因為太麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.06,0:11:53.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別動喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,買糖葫蘆了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.86,0:12:04.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.62,0:12:06.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.20,0:12:11.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來來 有希 別發呆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.67,0:12:16.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們來比賽 看誰撈的金魚最多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.22,0:12:24.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得想想方法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.73,0:12:36.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我現在就開始救你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.69,0:12:38.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都是好孩子 別亂動喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.82,0:12:41.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種東西小事一樁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.57,0:12:45.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很遺憾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.54,0:12:59.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眼睛 要看準金魚的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瞄準目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.71,0:13:02.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我撈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.30,0:13:05.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}我還能再抓上20條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.88,0:13:05.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝倉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.20,0:13:06.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}怎麼可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.84,0:13:06.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}這次是那條金魚哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.26,0:13:11.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在你看來 我肯定是個優柔寡斷的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.31,0:13:15.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.53,0:13:23.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.90,0:13:27.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不知道該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.07,0:13:35.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使知道前段時間的長門跟現在的長門不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.00,0:13:45.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人的感情也不是那麼簡單就能弄懂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.26,0:13:46.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在的長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.84,0:13:54.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該很明白自己在不知明狀況下被你疏離了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.11,0:14:10.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也很抱歉 沒能馬上反應過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我應該早就明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感到尷尬的不止是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門也是 因為我的行為而難受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.93,0:14:34.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以 是時候表白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那時候 沒能說出來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.61,0:14:42.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這次一定要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,開始了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玉屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.37,0:14:54.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.37,0:15:00.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能跟我來一下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.89,0:15:12.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我接下來要玩射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.27,0:15:20.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.73,0:15:21.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來比賽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.92,0:15:55.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說真的 被你表白的時候我一下子沒能理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.47,0:16:00.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為我不覺得自己有做出讓你想告白的努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.23,0:16:04.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊？你說什麼？我沒聽見啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.02,0:16:07.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說我哪裡好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.19,0:16:11.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼 我不懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.82,0:16:13.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也是啊 你不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.49,0:16:22.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了 這麼突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.83,0:16:27.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 給我聽好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.96,0:16:30.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先說好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.01,0:16:37.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是不會討厭長門的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.72,0:16:39.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.77,0:16:50.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以說 表白的回復只能是這個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.45,0:16:56.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.24,0:17:02.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我肯定早就喜歡你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我剛說的 聽到了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.74,0:17:34.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好 這就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.32,0:17:39.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 緊張死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.62,0:17:48.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也對 你那反應也是正常的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.71,0:17:54.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 不好意思 前段時間那麼冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.17,0:18:00.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖說有點強硬 但能說出心裡話 真舒暢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從現在開始就是平常的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肚子餓了 去吃點什麼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.13,0:18:35.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好啊 我也餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.63,0:18:37.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想吃什麼 我請你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.13,0:18:39.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.76,0:18:44.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別介意 反正春日會隨便找個理由讓我請客的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.64,0:18:46.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我要章魚燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.18,0:18:47.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.56,0:18:50.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有 那浴衣很合身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.40,0:18:56.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,終於說出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.33,0:19:10.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.54,0:19:11.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.13,0:19:12.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還想要別的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不了 足夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.80,0:19:20.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 你們去哪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.88,0:19:23.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有我的許可就離群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.18,0:19:24.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿虛 做為懲罰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.35,0:19:29.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請大家吃章魚燒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.52,0:19:30.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.65,0:19:34.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.65,0:19:36.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓你們久等了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.44,0:19:39.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 來遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.78,0:19:44.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝比奈學姐 那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.62,0:19:47.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你買了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.59,0:20:04.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暑假的最後 久違的社團後回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.89,0:20:07.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我突然發現了一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.81,0:20:09.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說是夏日集訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,結果卻去了海邊游泳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,山裡的試膽大冒險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.98,0:20:14.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,市民游泳池裡的玩樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天體觀測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玩了保齡球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.02,0:20:20.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有擊球中心跟夏日祭典
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.15,0:20:21.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是想起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.49,0:20:25.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像樣的文學活動一個都沒有做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.91,0:20:33.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因此 我想在文化祭裡出個小冊子或是接力小說什麼的 怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.08,0:20:36.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣的話 完全就是文化社了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.25,0:20:40.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們 連這個都忘記了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.76,0:20:42.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,開玩笑 開玩笑了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.43,0:20:48.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是跟涼宮說了的話肯定會來勁的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.10,0:20:50.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 那傢伙呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.97,0:20:51.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,外星人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.89,0:20:52.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,未來人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.73,0:20:53.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,異界人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.77,0:20:57.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超能者等一起跑出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.94,0:20:59.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 感覺好有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.77,0:21:02.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 要試著寫小說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.70,0:21:09.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天去長門家一起吃飯怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.95,0:21:12.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好主意 就這麼定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,順便一提 有什麼菜色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.83,0:21:15.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,關東煮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.50,0:21:18.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Summer關東煮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.59,0:21:20.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這麼熱的天吃關東煮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.71,0:21:21.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想搞忍耐大賽嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.92,0:21:26.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夏日裡吃關東煮 別有一番風味喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.51,0:21:33.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了 要變紅燈了 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.73,0:21:36.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.77,0:21:38.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有點羞澀的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.98,0:21:40.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門有希的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.41,0:23:20.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總感覺很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.21,0:23:24.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可思議的這麼想著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.72,0:23:33.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿虛 你有電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.39,0:23:34.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不說我也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.93,0:23:37.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.77,0:23:39.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.10,0:23:41.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿虛 你今天很閒對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.06,0:23:45.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給我兩點整在咖啡店裡集合 over
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.61,0:23:48.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我還什麼都沒說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.00,0:24:04.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說阿虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.63,0:24:06.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暑假要結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.38,0:24:07.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你作業做好了沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.46,0:24:09.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊

